cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

The paper deals with speech synthesis using deep neural networks and auto-encoders, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of a recurrent neural network also suggests a possible fit with the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SD).
